msg":"灘叔避債果part好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84fd3d1e1bd1b35e76e251caa6a2d840d2cdcbbc","tid":1011083,"uid":60136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T10:55:53.000Z","msg":"主題曲 好正氣<br />\n<br />\n當生活折磨　也暗中在慶賀<br />\n當生命折墮　良朋同樣滿座"},{"pid":"7bd474247928748e7451535409d25a87bcb86dcf","tid":1011083,"uid":43751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T11:03:13.000Z","msg":"仲有黃秋生"},{"pid":"dea7665ed3fbd2219ece505c9355d61e374cca66","tid":1011083,"uid":93998,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b18afb51773c74cf0982c9bd454797d373a7791a","tid":1011083,"uid":34760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T12:46:48.000Z","msg":"連子華自己都唔滿意就咪鬼推上去啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T11:55:59.000Z","msg":"佢要求咁高<br />\n佢自己唔滿意代表我哋唔可以欣賞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}